# LLM4Reading 密钥配置文件
# 复制此文件为 secrets.env 并填入你的实际密钥
# 注意：不要将 secrets.env 提交到版本控制系统

# ===========================================
# 必需的API密钥 (Required API Keys)
# ===========================================

# LLM API 密钥 (支持DeepSeek、OpenAI等)
# DeepSeek获取地址: https://platform.deepseek.com/
# OpenAI获取地址: https://platform.openai.com/
LLM_API_KEY=your_llm_api_key_here

# GitHub Personal Access Token
# 获取地址: GitHub Settings → Developer settings → Personal access tokens
# 需要权限: repo, workflow
GH_TOKEN=your_github_personal_access_token_here

# 邮箱应用专用密码 (不是登录密码!)
# QQ邮箱: 设置 → 账户 → 开启SMTP服务 → 获取授权码
# Gmail: 开启两步验证 → 生成应用专用密码
# 163邮箱: 设置 → POP3/SMTP/IMAP → 开启SMTP → 获取授权码
EMAIL_PASSWORD=your_email_app_password_here

# ===========================================
# 可选配置 (Optional)
# ===========================================


